		<title>Tools for Distributed Software Testing Teams</title>
		<link>https://www.softwaretestingmagazine.com/tools/tools-for-distributed-software-testing-teams/</link>
					<comments>https://www.softwaretestingmagazine.com/tools/tools-for-distributed-software-testing-teams/#respond</comments>
		
