		<link>https://www.softwaretestingmagazine.com/news/new-partnership-between-lambdatest-and-katalon/</link>
					<comments>https://www.softwaretestingmagazine.com/news/new-partnership-between-lambdatest-and-katalon/#respond</comments>
		
