		<link>https://www.softwaretestingmagazine.com/knowledge/how-to-prevent-reliably-damages-from-cyberattacks/</link>
					<comments>https://www.softwaretestingmagazine.com/knowledge/how-to-prevent-reliably-damages-from-cyberattacks/#respond</comments>
		
